{"tid":129364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭西鐵有兩個黑人拍我膊頭...","createTime":"2017-02-21T13:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T16:39:39.000Z","uid":75759,"like":1,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcca5a43ac9fb10e1adb413e51610d583bdcf3b","tid":129364,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"話係杜拜過黎旅遊，唔見咗行李銀包，叫我捭一舊水佢食老麥，又攞張唔知係咪報警備案嘅紀錄出黎（我無詳細睇）。<br />\n<br />\n我初頭都唔多信佢哋，叫佢哋跟我搭車去下個站，我直接幫佢買（我無講到明），到站後佢哋就話要攞錢搭翻朗屏食，有其他朋友響朗屏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我都好心捭咗100佢哋，而家再諗吓我好似上咗當<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有類似經歷可以屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：窮撚學生哥 CD-ROM 唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc91f7fc23eb4fe701ec250b48a3edc46383450","tid":129364,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"杜拜黎香港會冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地一日一架跑車都得啦"},{"pid":"248f2369b46cbc1bfd6b876d385af9f69402a40b","tid":129364,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"屌你好撚蠢"},{"pid":"add6abafc1dd5a603586e237b5c31a64024902e6","tid":129364,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"咁你而家想點撚樣<br />\n錢你就俾左佢"},{"pid":"f92d4f462081984e4c99e10e1bcbdca9c3bd3d3f","tid":129364,"uid":81177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"黎旅行點會住朗屏"},{"pid":"323e5d2fe15573ce91dfeb17a96a14c6f02ecb54","tid":129364,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"我都知我蠢<i