rvice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/001243_ccda6d9246c578f07214cfc821a863da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F001243_ccda6d9246c578f07214cfc821a863da.jpg&h=0ac8fb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報案紙係咪呢張？</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係啦 張紙大概係寫佢地比人打劫之類<br />\n但見過報案紙既人正常都唔撚會上當"},{"pid":"a11d8e8bc3f6f7e8f342ee13d20f572e3ee286f4","tid":129364,"uid":79758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/001243_ccda6d9246c578f07214cfc821a863da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F001243_ccda6d9246c578f07214cfc821a863da.jpg&h=0ac8fb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報案紙係咪呢張？</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係啦 張紙大概係寫佢地比人打劫之類<br />\n但見過報案紙既人正常都唔撚會上當</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7847741985460d2e5fb9d5a6bac666ef9e4b03","tid":129364,"uid":27273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"一模一樣，有一晚我係元朗街頭遇到，佢用英文講佢係自杜拜，唔見咗個iPhone同$5000現金，依家好肚餓，問我可唔可以俾少少錢佢食野，仲拎張報失紙出嚟。佢哋好醒目，張報失紙上面姓名、ID嘅位置已經用黑色筆遮住哂，睇佢張紙仲要好似過咗層膠係上面咁。因為夜晚，我好驚一拎個銀包出嚟就俾佢搶走，之後我話無。等佢調轉頭我再拎咗$20話我得咁多，嗱嗱聲俾佢就走咗。<br />\n雖然都心知佢好大機會係呃人、不過$20如果佢真係好餓嘅話都起碼可以買個豬柳強頂肚嘅。"},{"pid":"e822c6c91fda750fdd27ad592da0b2072e1561a7","tid":129364,"uid":74277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"啲nigger唔係窮到黎香港窮撚地方搵食啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438dac39f3bf24ef576c93dddc57592f455e92e3","tid":129364,"uid":32437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"弱智仔"},{"pid":"6cb0cd50a5484a83eafa332edab70621aacb3e8a","tid":129364,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"都叫做左善事 無蝕<br />\n個黑人會有報應姐<img src=\"/ass