lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我都好心捭咗100佢哋，而家再諗吓我好似上咗當<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有類似經歷可以屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：窮撚學生哥 CD-ROM 唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了欺騙善心之外，<br />\n是否還利用了人們「投桃報李」的投機心態？"},{"pid":"b784d9f83dcb9d30275c1e90c6747485cf8e7473","tid":129364,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"100可以買10次六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f041512ccd2e7abb11264c970777b2a72d0e50f5","tid":129364,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"蠢撚到"},{"pid":"d5384ba1cff2df1592df55c1254405171ce8a631","tid":129364,"uid":15936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"樓主我都冇錢食晏，你可唔可以俾$1000我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fe7099d3fba02ca42296f275c84f8e396e69fa","tid":129364,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"唔俾我都怕俾佢地吊住尾<br />\n虐打到半死點算"},{"pid":"a71dbb3f2f4a21ee6c73d9b294e8773594bc4a36","tid":129364,"uid":38840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"衰撚過啲魔術黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bd67e8ac72ec7dd7a5316272047e9b184eaa69","tid":129364,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>17歲果年<br />\n有一晚約左班fd食飯<br />\n我收工之後就去灣仔join佢地<br />\n我出左灣仔地鐵站之後<br />\n有個自稱日本來既交流生問我機場點去<br />\n我話唔知 但當時未夠鐘食飯就陪佢周圍搵巴士<br />\n跟住佢話自己趕飛機返日本 要搭的士去機場<br />\n但佢唔夠錢 問我借<br />\n我當時銀包都冇乜錢 就俾左$100佢<br />\n佢寫左個email俾我 叫我聯絡佢 話返到日本之後寄返錢俾我<br />\n之後就上左的士<br />\n<br />\n最後我冇email 返佢<br />\n當時個心抱住萬一佢真急需要呢$100既話<br />\n即使有機會俾人呃都會借<br />\n<br />\n個人又蠢又心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師兄文筆幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">個故ok</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我懷疑我識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ce6b538b90421feaea259e635dba61c97f4161","tid":129364,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"咁多on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b44706dc272ea272979cb1f59519af20f57356","tid":129364,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"之前尖沙咀有個韓妹問我借$100<br />\n見佢對腳幾白幾滑就畀咗佢"},{"pid":"59049752d6277945e2559fd926501a54173dcd1b","tid":129364,"uid":64056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n元朗屯門好多拎住form8、酷刑聲稱、偷渡落嚟既黑鬼<br />\n個個月政府已經送幾千蚊佢地洗<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母好心你就醒d<br />\n唔識英文對答、淆底你就走啦<br />\n俾人拋兩下就俾錢人<br />\n一係你就記低張超雄議員辦事處個電話<br />\n叫黑鬼打俾難民之父"},{"pid":"e5559a0e886eec2f8aa764e07eaa72cc26e0e910","tid":129364,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"假難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7396bd35b462da7c53bfa815f87fc0571d4edd55","tid":129364,"uid